\sum\limits_{n = 1}^\infty  {{b_n}\frac{L}{2}{\delta _{nm}} = \left\{ {\begin{array}{*{20}{c}}   0&{n \ne m} \\    {{b_m}\frac{L}{2}}&{n = m}  \end{array}} \right.}
